		REPLACE CHIAVE_R  WITH "TOC"
		REPLACE RIGAT     WITH REPLICATE(PUB_CAROR,80) 
		REPLACE RIGA      WITH SPACE(50)
		REPLACE CHIAVE    WITH 999999

